==English==
===Noun===
'''outfield'''
#{{baseball}} The region of the [[field]] between the [[infield]] and the outer fence
#: ''He hit a long fly ball to the '''outfield''' in the [[gap]] to left.''
#{{cricket}} The region of the field roughly [[outside]] of the [[wicket-keeper]], [[slip]]s, [[gully]], [[point]], [[cover]], [[mid off]], [[mid on]], [[midwicket]] and [[square leg]]

